
roomenter {"";
	checktoggle 236;
	smirk %n;
	say I believe you are trying to find me....aren't you?;
}

roomenter {"";
	checktoggle 244;
	smile %n;
	say So Gandolfo sent you back <R>right<1>?;
}

say {"right";
	checktoggle 244;
	whisper %n I understand...;
	grumble;
	say This is the thing that frightens you most...I can see into your soul.;
	say This is your last chance to quit for your fear will scar your soul for;
	say as long as you exist. If you wish to give up say you <R>can't<1>, if;
	say you will do this last deed then say I <R>can<1>.;
}

say { "yes";
	checktoggle 236;
	say Who sends you to me?;
}
 
say {"forsaken";
	checktoggle 236;
	say Forsaken is a fool, and is very shifty. I have no idea why Gandalfo;
	say has any respect for him. Let me guess...he gave you something for me?;
}

give {"31358"; 
	checktoggle 236;
	untoggle 236;
	toggle 237;
	nod %n;
	say O.k. Here is what you must do...;
	whisper %n You must find a great reptile in the southern lands known;
	whisper %n as the Veldt. This lizard is rare and it is known to great;
	whisper %n practitioners to possess great protective powers. I also believe;
	whisper %n that the hide of this lizard has life leeching powers that can help;
	whisper %n keep you alive in times of need.;
}

say {"veldt";
	checktoggle 237;
	say Goddamn it! You are what level? And your a Shaman?!?!;
	say To hell with you if you cant figure out what to do next.;
	say Get going! I will not stay here for long.;
}

say {"reptile";
	link say veldt;
}

say {"lizard";
	link say veldt;
}

give {"31361";
	checktoggle 237;
	untoggle 237;
	toggle 238;
	tell %n Good. It's about time.;
	load 31359;
	tell %n I will join the plank and hide together and then you must give it;
	tell %n to Gandolfo as soon as possible.;
	toroom $n lies down on the ground.;
	toroom $n carefully places the plank of wood on his chest.;
	toroom $n begins to moan.;
	toroom $n places the lizard hide on top of the plank of wood.;
	shout APLOXIMINE PRETENCUAR! BYGOMINE XEBECULA PROM FORTANG!!!!;
	toroom A feirce bolt of energy from the sky strikes the chest of $n!;
	toroom $n shakes and twinges as the energy bolt courses through his body!;
	toroom $n pants and gasps for breath.;
	say It...is...done;
	say Go now and give this to Gandolfo.;
	give cover %n;
	say Hurry! It must be dont before the loa's energy leaves the plank!;
	say GO!!!;
}

say {"can't";
	checktoggle 244;
	untoggle 244;
	untoggle 233;
	toggle 246;
	say Very well...You are done coward.;
}

say {"can";
	checktoggle 244;
	untoggle 244;
	toggle 245;
	say Very well %n, however before you face your fear I would like to know something.;
	say Which loa do you favor the most?;
	say <R>Ogun<1> - loa of metal and iron?;
	say <R>Obatala<1> - loa of the clouds?;
	say <R>Yemaya<1> - loa of the oceans?;
	say <R>Oya<1> - loa of the winds and hurricanes?;
	say <R>Oshun<1> - loa of the rivers?;
	say <R>Chango<1> - loa of sky?;
	say The importance of this question will prove to be of great importance later...;
	say so choose wisely.;
}

say {"ogun";
	checktoggle 245;
	say Very well...You will face the evil in your heart!;
	say If you succeed this test then you go straight back to Gandolfo and tell;
	say him you have killed your own father's spirit!;
	cackle; 
	load 31351;
	toroom $n claps his hands and suddenly a spirit materializes.;
	loadmob 31314;
	give stone spirit-father;
	say Now we must kill you...Sorry.;
	kill %n;
}

